cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with moving object detection in video, which is a common problem in computer vision. The use of background modeling techniques and edge detection algorithms is also a common approach in this field. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the evaluation of the detection using frame-based metrics, which is related to machine learning and data analysis, hence cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories. The use of algorithms for object detection and segmentation can also be related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and information retrieval (cs.IR) categories.
